divs: sighting detailsit is 10:38pm on 4\16\13 (pacific time)as i am writing this report in salem, oregon. for the past few months i have been seeing starlike objects moving in various speeds in the night sky. it seems there are more every night, but the most i have seen is tonight and i am still seeing them as i type this. there are also a lot of helicopters and low hovering planes just as long as i have been seeing these objects. some are very bright and moving in weird paths, and some are so small they look like ants in the sky, and loo exactly like stars, but since stars dont move, then i know they aren't stars haha. anyone notice these?
Object Flight Path: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering,Other
